---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | Rob Williams BJJ – South Brisbane"
  description="Rob Williams BJJ is Queensland's first Pedro Sauer Jiu-Jitsu Association affiliate. Learn about Master Pedro Sauer, his philosophy, and what makes our academy different."
>

  <Header />

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="page-hero relative flex items-end px-6 pb-16 pt-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full">
      <p class="text-brand-red uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Pedro Sauer Association</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-3">
        Gracie Jiu Jitsu.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white/80">
        Taught the Right Way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PEDRO SAUER ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brand-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Bio + photo -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand-red uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Master Pedro Sauer</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
            One of the Most Technical Coaches in the World
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Master Pedro Sauer holds an 8th degree Rickson Gracie coral belt and is recognised globally
            as one of the most professional and technical coaches in the world of Gracie Jiu Jitsu.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
            His association encompasses over 250 affiliates internationally, with a strong presence across
            Australia — particularly in Victoria and New South Wales. Rob Williams BJJ has the honour of
            being the first academy in Queensland to represent Master Sauer and his legacy.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Training within the Pedro Sauer Association means our students learn Jiu Jitsu that connects
            directly to the Gracie family lineage — the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu — through one of
            its most respected representatives.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/Pedro-Sauer-Shaka.jpg" alt="Master Pedro Sauer" class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Accolades row -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-brand-red font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Belt Rank</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">8th Degree Coral Belt</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Awarded by Rickson Gracie</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-brand-red font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Association Reach</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">250+ Affiliates</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Across Australia and internationally</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-brand-red font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Queensland Representation</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">Rob Williams BJJ</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">First and only QLD affiliate</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PHILOSOPHY ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-brand-red uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">The Philosophy</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Technical Precision Over Raw Intensity</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          The Pedro Sauer approach prioritises technical proficiency above all else — especially for beginners.
          Intensity is deliberately limited while students are learning, so that correct movement patterns
          are built before pressure is applied.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          This is the same "Crawl, Walk, Run" methodology used by US Navy SEALs — and it's how every
          student progresses at Rob Williams BJJ, whether they're four years old or forty.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The result is Jiu Jitsu that lasts. Students train safely, build real technique, and can continue
          doing Jiu Jitsu for life — not just until their body gives out.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
        {[
          { step: '01', title: 'Crawl', desc: 'Learn slowly and safely. Intensity is kept low while technique is absorbed. No ego, no rushing.' },
          { step: '02', title: 'Walk', desc: 'Build timing and flow. Techniques start to connect under light resistance.' },
          { step: '03', title: 'Run', desc: 'Train with full intensity on a solid foundation. Your technique holds because it was built right.' },
        ].map(({ step, title, desc }) => (
          <div class="flex gap-5 bg-brand-gray border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-brand-red font-mono text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">{step}</p>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold mb-1">{title}</h3>
              <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PHOTO BREAK ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="px-6 py-0 md:pb-10 bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 h-[560px]">
      <img src="/Pedro.jpg" alt="Master Pedro Sauer" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center rounded-lg" />
      <img src="/Pedro.Rob.jpg" alt="Rob Williams with Master Pedro Sauer" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-bottom rounded-lg" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── COMMUNITY MISSION ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-24 md:pt-28 px-6 bg-brand-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-brand-red uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Our Mission</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-8">More Than Martial Arts</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        The Pedro Sauer Association's main focus is to create stronger, safer and a more healthy community.
        Beyond self-defence and confidence-building, we believe Jiu Jitsu has the power to transform lives.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Every instructor affiliated with Master Sauer is held to a standard that reflects his legacy —
        a friendly attitude, respect for all training partners regardless of age or ability,
        and a commitment to making Jiu Jitsu accessible for life.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
        {[
          { icon: '🤝', title: 'Respect', desc: 'Every partner on the mat is treated with respect — always.' },
          { icon: '🌏', title: 'Community', desc: 'Building stronger, safer people in South Brisbane and Logan.' },
          { icon: '🥋', title: 'Longevity', desc: 'Training that’s sustainable so you can do Jiu Jitsu for life.' },
        ].map(({ icon, title, desc }) => (
          <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-7">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">{icon}</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── TEAM CTA ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-brand-dark border-t border-white/10 text-center">
    <p class="text-brand-red uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Meet the Coaches</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The People Behind the Mat</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto">
      Learn about Professor Rob Williams and the team who bring Master Sauer's philosophy to life every class.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/team" class="bg-brand-red hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded transition inline-block">
        Meet Our Team
      </a>
      <a href="/#free-trial" class="border border-white/30 hover:border-white text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded transition inline-block">
        Book a Free Trial
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── FOOTER ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <footer class="bg-brand-dark border-t border-white/10 py-14 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-3">ROB WILLIAMS <span class="text-brand-red">BJJ</span></p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Authentic Gracie Jiu Jitsu self-defence academy.<br />
          South Brisbane · Meadowbrook QLD
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-white/80 mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Contact</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/60 text-sm">
          <li><a href="tel:0421729868" class="hover:text-white transition">📞 0421 729 868</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:robwilliamsgz@gmail.com" class="hover:text-white transition">✉️ robwilliamsgz@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=3/45+Nealdon+Dr+Meadowbrook+QLD+4131" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white transition">
              📍 3/45 Nealdon Dr, Meadowbrook QLD 4131
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-white/80 mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Quick Links</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/programs" class="hover:text-white transition">Programs</a></li>
          <li><a href="/timetable" class="hover:text-white transition">Timetable & Pricing</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/team" class="hover:text-white transition">Our Team</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#free-trial" class="hover:text-white transition">Free Trial</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 text-center text-white/30 text-xs">
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} Rob Williams BJJ. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>
